Other tools¶

Course Structure¶

  • Lectures (also recorded beforehand):
    • Tue, hours 5+6, and Thu, hours 1+2
    • Before/after each lecture: Read in Think Python (book)
    • Topics alternate: Python Software Engineering
  • Guided lab sessions
    • Tue, hours 7+8, and Thu, hours 3+4
    • Online support through Teams channels
  • Exercises (individual): 6x, best 5 count (5%); see schedule
    • Autograded by Momotor (need to score at least 80%)
  • Homework Assignments (in pairs, except HA-0; 5%+10%+30%); (see schedule)
  • Final Test (50%; grade at least 5.0)
